NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
S.L., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
L.M., Defendant. In the Matter of M.A.M.-L., a Minor, Respondent. C-166 September Term 2017
079258 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 16, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000159-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
